title.narrative: DSIF - Ghana - Lavender Hill Sludge Treatment Project

description.narrative: The project will provide an effective low-cost faecal sludge treatment plant at Lavender Hill, Accra. An existing pilot plant nearby has showcased the effectiveness of the suggested treatment technology and its appropriateness in a Ghanaian context.
